==English==
===Etymology===
from the name ''Angiospermae''

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#(''botany'') A member of the [[plant]] group characterized by having [[ovule]]s enclosed in an [[ovary]]; the [[angiosperms]] or [[flower]]ing plants: the ''[[Angiospermae]]'', ''[[Magnoliophyta]]'', ''[[Magnoliopsida]]'', etc.

